PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Denis Losier, of Moncton, New Brunswick, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian National Railway Company to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Yvon Poitras, whose term has expired.

precis:
Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of Denis Losier,
of Moncton, New Brunswick, as a director of the Board of Directors of the
Canadian National Railway Company to hold office during pleasure for a term
of three years, in the place of Yvon Poitras, whose term has expired.
